scopeContent.description:
'Photograph of a bed of mushrooms grown in a wooden building. A big cluster of medium sized mushrooms in top left hand corner. Three large mushrooms on the right of wooden support. Large clusters of all sizes on the right of these. In the centre front, one large mushroom with two small round ones underneath it, with a straw raised on them. In front of these, five large mushrooms together. On the left of them some white mushrooms with frill round stalk. In bottom right corner, the top half of two mushrooms'.

scopeContent.description:
'Photograph of a bed of mushrooms grown in a wooden building. Heaps of all sizes of mushrooms all over the bed, excepting small part on the top left. Six or seven small white mushrooms at the foot of a wooden support in the centre, a string of small white with a few large ones branch off from the right of these and lead up to a large round cluster of small mushrooms. In front of this some larger ones. Almost in the top right corner, a large misshapen white mushroom. Along the bottom, a continuance of clusters of all sizes, three mushrooms of which have bent stalks on which are shown the frill'.

scopeContent.description:
'Photograph of sixteen headed broccoli-winter cauliflowers called 'Holmes' Choice'. Twelve arranged in long white willow basket on wooden stand and four in row in front. At the top and back of broccoli are their leaves in an upright position. Two of the biggest leaves are hanging over to the left side and one next to these on the right is upright. Some leaves are on the ground in front of those in front row. The second broccoli from the right in front row is very compact, has several small leaves growing round it, and one leaf in front is broken and hangs down in front. A large compact broccoli is just behind. There are four in bottom row, five in second, four in third, and three in fourth at top'.
